Understanding AI, ML, DL, and LLMs is extremely important in cybersecurity because:

* AI is used in threat detection systems
* ML helps identify unusual patterns (anomalies) in network traffic
* DL enables advanced malware detection and behavior analysis
* LLMs can be used for automated analysis, report generation, and even attack simulations

